    "description": "<strong>About</strong><br>DIVE is an atmospheric 3rd person shooter with light puzzles and platforming.  This demo is a vertical slice to showcase the general combat, feel, and atmosphere, with a &quot;greybox&quot; approach allow more development time on systems and gameplay.<br><br><strong>Developer Notes</strong><br>This has been fairly long solo project (stretching about 3x over the original 6 month estimate), but it ended up being so enjoyable to design, build, and playtest that I honestly had a difficult time stopping.  For the project itself, my goal is to take a long break from this -- as it's been very much exhausting -- and use the lessons-learned on bringing other projects to life.",
